abstract: Former champion Lee Janzen will have another shot at United States Open golf tournament after earning spot in New York sectional qualifier.
lead_paragraph: Janzen, 50, won the event in 1993 and 1998. He earned the first of four spots available at the New York sectional qualifier.

headline.main: Lee Janzen Qualifies for United States Open
